	References
	----------
	[NMI13]
		McDaid, Aaron F., Derek Greene, and Neil Hurley. "Normalized Mutual Information to Evaluate Overlapping
		Community Finding Algorithms." ArXiv:1110.2515 [Physics], August 2, 2013. http://arxiv.org/abs/1110.2515.
